dct_description_sm: Dated from the earliest atlas in which the map was issued in this state. Differs from previous states by changes in placenames. Shows boundaries, rivers, roads, woods, parks and settlements. Relief shown pictorially. London meridian.
dct_publisher_sm: [London] : Sold by Abel Swale, Awnsham and Iohn Churchill, [1722]
